Interface SummaryContributer<T extends DataObject>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppUserFactory, CertificateComposite, DirectoryComposite, EmailNameFinder, MultiKeyComposite, PublicKeyComposite, SingleKeyComposite

    public interface SummaryContributer<T extends DataObject>
    Interface for providing summary information. This is usually implemented by a DataObjectFactory or Composite and is intended to build a Map of attributes that provide summary information about the target object. These will usually be added to a Table so the data should be of a type that can be displayed by Tables The keys should be display text.

    spb
